headline: Gen to Announce Fiscal 2025 Fourth Quarter and Full-Year Results on May 6, 2025
summary: Gen Digital Inc. (NASDAQ: GEN) today announced that its fiscal year 2025 fourth quarter and full-year financial results will be released Tuesday, May 6, 2025, after market close. Following the press release, Gen management will host a conference call and webcast at 2 p.m. PT / 5 p.m. ET.
